dct_title_s: Nouveau plan routier de la ville & faubourgs de Paris, divisé en 12 arrondissemens ou municipalités
dct_description_sm: Margins include alphabetical indexes to streets and church parishes, and tables containing assorted civic information. Includes inset: Département de la Seine, divisé en 12 arrondissemens ou municipalités. Originally issued in covers, 23 x 15 cm.
dct_publisher_sm: A Paris : chez Esnauts et Rapilly, rue Saint Jacques, à la Ville de Coutances, No. 285 An IX [1800?]
